heyy people!
yea, so i'm up early 2day, for a saturday...and I'm bored...so, thought I'd update...anywho, lots going on in my life right now! yay me! lmao stef! well, last night, me and laura had the technical rehearsal 4 dance, and we were real bad, considering we both don't know one part of the dance well at all...but the whole class sucked so we don't feel bad, but our teach was actually really nice about it and she was like "don't worry, this is what rehearsals r 4" so...yea...but we still felt pretty bad...haha but, lauras mommy brought her kfc, but she was pissed because there was no ketchup...and she whined...a lot, 4 a few minutes, lmao still luv ya laur...but then some1z mom bought us pizza! nd me, laura and a girl in our class gabby were like the first out there, lmao...hmmm, so, yea, we have dance 2day, and I think Liz is keeping us late, if possible, because, we "know" what we have to work on...lol...oh boy...ha, but our dance is soooo much better than the other hip-hop class, and they get to go last, its not fair, we should like be the end, but whatever...the audience will just be dissapointed when they get to the other class...haha, no im horrible, they were good, i just like ours better...oh yea, and if she can get tickets, I get 2 go 2 the AMERICAN IDOL CONCERT with Laura and her mommy and her cousin and her aunt? I think, yea, I have 2 ask her about that one, but I am all excited! we are soooo making shirts that say how much we love ANTHONY FEDEROV!!!!! hes so damn cute its rediculous! And I made up the cutest nickname ever if I do say so myself...a-rov...hell yes! and we need to stick ryan's name on a hat or something because we luv him 2...alright, yea, we're a little pathetic, but so what...hmmm ok, so what else? hmmm...we just got the huge english portfolio 2 do, which counts as a final, plus an italian project thats due soon...so, I'm doing most of the italian project today, and then the english paper, and then I'm gonna start the portfolio tomorrow or next weekend...since its not due till june...anyways, I guess thats it, so I'm gonna go...so much 2 do, so little time...leave comments, since I rock...<3XoXo<3

hey peopleee!
ok, so yea, this is my first update on this live journal, I had one, and it got messed up because my computer is strange, so, yea...anyways, 2day was totally awesome! School hasn't been bad lately, shocking enough, and I've been really getting into chorus stuff...oh yea, and brittany did too...ha! luv ya britt!!! ok, so, I went to school, and then I went to women's choir!!! oh yea baby! me and brittany totally rock btw because we finally got the last note in Music in my Soul!!!! ha! we like did a high five when we hit it, and it was really loud 2...yea, we're lame...very, but its all good...oh yea, and my lovely friend rosa decided to step on the back of my sandal yesterday as we were going up the stairs, and i fell up...not to mention that she did this twice, and I couldn't get it back on! I'm such a spaz, but this one wasn't fully my fault, Rosa did it!!! ha! but stefanie has fallen up 2 so she was like so careful today, it was histerical!!! hmm, is that it? oh yea, one tree hill was amazingly amazing last night! but then again, when is it not? yea, so stef was on the fone with me not too long ago, and she was singing the damn chicken song...and it got very annoying...but I luv her anyway, I guess, somewhat...ha! just kidding stef-a-lef-a-ding-dong! ha!!!!!!!! Dave: don't u love how my mother and my wife say my name in the same tone?! HA!!!!!!! SOOOOOO DAMN FUNNY!!! The Ricky song I made up! ha! Ricky, Sticky, Licky, Mickey....Dz ha!!! oh yea, and I have my dance practice rehearsal thingy nd me and Laura r totally gonna rock! uhh, maybe not but it was worth a try...anyway, yea, that was a bunch of insiders that no1 is really gonna get...but its cool...so yea, I guess thats really about it, and since its my first update, i'll give a shoutout to some awesomely awesome people...hannah,laura,jee,bri,shannon and BRITTANIA! ha! you people rock...
